-------- Day 3 --------
🇷🇸 Serbia 🇷🇸
🇧🇦 Bosnia & Herzegovina 🇧🇦
🇲🇪 Montenegro 🇲🇪
🚂🚂🚂 Belgrade - Bar railway 🚂🚂🚂
------------------------------------------------
Almost 500km long connection between former Yugoslavian capital and the very coast of Adriatic in Montenegro. 10 hours long ride, 254 tunnels  and 435 bridges, stretching through landscapes hard to be described by words or captured by any camera. It's just something to experience, a "must do" position on the lifetime bucket list if such exist. You can glue your face to the window and/or open up the poorly secured rear door as we did and enjoy the sceneries for hours. Just beware of the conductors & don't jump ;d. Unforgettable.
